25 instruction on student instructional days (as described in
26 IC 20-30-2-2) for a school year as required under IC 20-30-2-3 to
27 sell a covered building described in subsection (a) at a purchase
28 price mutually agreed to by the parties.
29 (c) If a sale described in subsection (b) is not made within the
30 one (1) year period set forth in subsection (b), the governing body
31 shall make the covered school building available for lease or
32 purchase by a charter school or state educational institution in the
33 manner described in section 3 of this chapter.
